'''tolpe''' is the [[Telerin]] number "eighteen"<ref>{{VT|48}}</ref>
==Etymology==
Possible [[Primitive Elvish]] *''tolokwê''. The [[Sundocarmë|Root]] for "eight" is [[TOLOD]] and we see the suffix ''[[-pe]]'' "-teen".
==Cognates==
*[[Quenya]] ''[[toloque]]''
